chat.msg: hey, estas listo?
si
Estamos en el punto de partida con una ramita a nuestra izquierda que conduce a una pequeña isla con un tigre.
¿A dónde vamos desde aquí?
we go over the bridge towards the parrots head
We walk northwest, to the point where the parrot is perched on a tree on the big island.
And now what do I do, friend?
go around the parrot, near the elephant and cross over the rock bridge
okay. so, i'm heading past the parrot, walking near the elephant, and then crossing the rock bridge to the island with the frog on it
i can see a crocodile on my left from here. are we on the right track?
yes, walk on top of the crocodile and go up to cross by the rocks near the giraffe
ha, brave move! i'm now walking on top of the crocodile, up to the rocks close to the giraffe
from here, can i now see the snake? where to next, cap?
cross over the stick and the snake to the treasure
alright, passing the stick and the snake
i see the treasure! *finished* quite the adventure eh?

chat.msg: hey!!! ya comenzamos?
yes!
great! Initially, walk to the left and cross the path towards a flower hut
but don't go there, make a u and go back to the white dog. ready?
i am at the white dog
perfect! now cross over that wooden branch towards the south and keep moving down the map
you'll soon spot another white dog. you following?
yes i am at the white dog by the bottom right
fantastic! now, amble over the mat near the bowl of berries and continue walking west
you got it right?
yes i am on the mat
rock on! now, see that wooden branch? cross it towards the north
that's your next mission. go for it!
i crossed and am by a bush and a bike path
great job! circle around that bush from the right, moving towards the florist stand
you see it?
yes
awesome! now, turn left and pass under the stand until you reach the big bridge
ok
made it to the bridge? keep going straight past it to the west
don't even worry about those cyclists, you're doing great!
okay done
cool! did you see two elderly folks reading newspapers by the bench? move south for a bit between them and the wooden branch nearby
awaiting your update!
yes i am at the branch
great job! now, walk east between the branch and the bush nearby
keep going!
okay
you're doing amazing! just a few steps east, did you see a brown young deer?
yes
awesome! that's your final stop
good job mate, you navigated the path like a champ!

chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to start?
yes! Starting at the tent, walk south to see the puppy
ok, i see the cute puppy sitting next to the fire
what's next?
go under the puppy, and the over the fire and stop between the fire and mushrooms
done, i'm now between the fire pit and the red mushroom
what's up next?
now walk onto the trail, on top of the hood of the blue car
cool, i'm now standing on the blue car's hood, what's next on the agenda?
make a u-turn, walking back towards the fire, but at the fork, so south instead of west
alrighty, i walked south at the fork
i can see a blue telescope in front of me. where to now?
go under the telescope, cutting between it and the bush to the right
done, i cut between the telescope and the bush
i can now see some rocks and a wooden house. what now, mate?
walk over the rocks to the house
i've crossed the rocks, now standing in front of the wooden house
*finished* is that right?

chat.msg: hola, you ready?
yes
awesome! start by heading southwest under the first palm tree, then make a right, cross the second tree, and take a sharp left before the third palm tree
keep going south
ok i am by the dog
cute, right? now, walk to the left of the puppy, then swing slightly to the left and then make a hard right heading south
i am by the biggest rock
you're doing great! now, navigate between the big rock to your left and the smaller one on your right
keep going until you reach the coast. make sure to enjoy the view!
am at the coast in front of the crab
hi there mr. crab! turn right and walk with the big rock on your left, heading west in the water
watch your step. splash!
okay no what
now
when you reach the third rock, look out for a shark
make a sharp right at that point. it's quite an adventure, isn't it?
head back to dry land, navigating between the medium rock and the colorful ball then continue moving north
good job staying sharp!
i am north of the rock and ball
perfect position! now bear slightly left but keep a good pace north-west
notice the red tent and a bigger speaker? aim to pass between them
i am between them
great, now circle around the tent following its curve, and then head south straight towards the water again
okay
just when you think you're going to hit the water, make a right turn and go under the red kayak
try not to trip over!
i am under the kayak
perfect! now, make a 90 degree turn to the right, head north alongside the kayak until you find a small green bush
bit of a riddle isn't it?
